window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>An alien warrior has made me an offer I can’t refuse. In exchange, he can do what he wants with me for one week. </b></p> <p>I want a child, but that’s impossible now that Earth men are sterile. Then, a ping from a distant planet reaches us. Aliens are real, and they’re interested in getting to know Earth women better.</p> <p>The Xilans fall into an insatiable urge once every three years. It's called the Slaking. There aren’t enough females to give them what they need, so like many Earth women, I sign up. For one week, I’ll make an alien happy, and in exchange, I get a child. As long as I keep my heart of out of the equation, things should go fine, right?</p> <p>But when an intergalactic war erupts, we must fight for our very survival.</p> <p><i>Alien Commander’s Mate</i> is book one in the Fated Mates of the Xilan Warrior series. It features aliens who look and act alien, heated plot lines, and a guaranteed HEA.</p>"; 
